{"tid":534092,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"長者都有過情人節嘅權利","createTime":"2018-01-19T12:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T14:54:47.000Z","uid":82070,"like":40,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"29d7cbcf1feb550e182b8806a062ce31fbfab573","tid":534092,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:41:40.000Z","msg":"成日見到班偽廢青一去到情人節就打卡吹奏愛情 (利申︰我都係其中一個)<br />\n<br />\n然後落樓下見到啲公公婆婆一齊行路嘅背影，我覺得好sweet好難得<br />\n<br />\n但好少有人幫佢地影下相、留記念<br />\n<br />\n所以我諗咗好耐，黎緊2月10號想搞個長者情侶攝影活動<br />\n<br />\n希望長者年紀就算大咗，都可以同後生仔一樣感受一下節日既甜蜜<br />\n<br />\n有冇人會想Join？<br />\n<br />\n會幫長者化妝、cosplay、整手工<br />\n<br />\n超級需要人手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有興趣嘅可以聯絡樓主 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://telegram.me/Ching1165\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.me%2FChing1165&d=OTMKY0medqEF%2Bc%2Bl%2F%2FVY1dr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=89de3dc8\" target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.me/Ching1165</a>"},{"pid":"606ad1608010aca2475dfc81c60f70e188e64450","tid":534092,"uid":82070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:16:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"71349d1aeab69a19fc64a0442f1bff4da36272c7","tid":534092,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:34:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"29eac2f857c159e03174c71c724862fb756334bb","tid":534092,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T14:04:38.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n認真想做"},{"pid":"2f66199e8b33f323e508b47f7197c2e97faab75a","tid":534092,"uid":67485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T02:26:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"005ac7eb01528ddc49567db8074023e5d0d8ffcd","tid":534092,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T07:06:05.000Z","msg":"巴打會唔會可以幫手整福袋﹖<br />\n<br />\n因為我想整個情人節福袋，送比班公公婆婆"},{"pid":"15e6fc4f